~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : shemote                                   ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : shemote <action preformed>

   This command allows a user to "shout"(broadcast to every other 
   user in the talker, provided they are not ignoring shouts) an 
   action.  Similar to the .emote command, except that all users can 
   see it.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : shout, emote, pemote
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
